I'M INTERVIEWING MRS. FAIGA ROZA POLAK: F.A.I.G.A.,

00:01:03.498 --> 00:01:06.098
P.O.L.A.K. WHOSE MAIDEN NAME

00:01:06.098 --> 00:01:07.531
WAS DUB.

00:01:07.531 --> 00:01:09.032
MY NAME IS BRONNIE TAIT

00:01:09.032 --> 00:01:12.865
WE'RE IN MELBOURNE AUSTRALIA, AND THE INTERVIEW WILL BE CONDUCTED IN YIDDISH.

00:01:18.885 --> 00:01:21.152
tsum ershte, dayn nomen.

00:01:21.183 --> 00:01:25.014
ikh heys Polak, Feyge Roza,

00:01:25.181 --> 00:01:27.047
geboyrn Dub,

00:01:27.145 --> 00:01:29.534
Rokhele.

00:01:29.545 --> 00:01:31.612
un ven hostu geboyrn geven?

00:01:31.581 --> 00:01:34.452
ikh bin geboyrn eyn toyznt nayn hundert zibn

00:01:34.492 --> 00:01:36.667
 akht un tsvontsik,

00:01:36.723 --> 00:01:38.410
in september nayn.

00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:40.255
in Tetsh.

00:01:41.010 --> 00:01:44.088
dos hot geheysn ZAKARPATSLA UKRAINA.

00:01:44.164 --> 00:01:47.161
ven ikh bin geboyrn iz es gevezn Tshekhay.

00:01:47.218 --> 00:01:49.345
Tshekhoslovakye.

00:01:49.097 --> 00:01:51.564
un vos iz geven di nomen fun shtetl.

00:01:51.612 --> 00:01:52.547
Tetsh.

00:01:53.497 --> 00:01:55.197
un vi alt bistu yetst?

00:01:55.169 --> 00:01:58.063
ikh bin yetst nayn um zekhtsik yor alt.

00:01:58.631 --> 00:02:01.431
un vos iz geven di nomen fun dayn foter?

00:02:01.562 --> 00:02:04.423
mayn tate hot geheysn Gershn Dub.

00:02:04.384 --> 00:02:06.818
un ven hot er geboyrn gevorn?

00:02:06.558 --> 00:02:09.980
er iz geboyrn eyn toyznt nayn hundert eyns,

00:02:11.290 --> 00:02:13.513
in yuni finef.

00:02:14.110 --> 00:02:15.810
un vu?

00:02:16.224 --> 00:02:19.685
in Vermezif.

00:02:20.171 --> 00:02:22.037
un dayn muter?

00:02:21.709 --> 00:02:26.893
mayn mame iz geboyrn eyn, zi hot geheysn Eynhorn Etl,

00:02:28.060 --> 00:02:29.008
Etshe.

00:02:29.369 --> 00:02:32.951
un zi iz geboyrn eyn toyznt nayn hundert zibn,

00:02:33.189 --> 00:02:37.962
der date veys ikh nisht pinktlekh, in Popleshe.

00:02:38.756 --> 00:02:40.922
du host gehat brider un shvester?

00:02:40.919 --> 00:02:43.465
yo ikh hob gehat zeks brider,

00:02:44.584 --> 00:02:46.303
ale yinger fun mir,

00:02:47.174 --> 00:02:51.343
un eyn shvesterl, vos zi iz geshtorbn, iz zi geven di drite.

00:02:52.780 --> 00:02:55.246
vos iz geven di nomen fun di ershte?

00:02:55.304 --> 00:02:56.558
di ershte

00:02:56.870 --> 00:02:58.136
nokh mir

00:02:59.083 --> 00:03:00.637
hot geheysn Zise.

00:03:01.930 --> 00:03:07.504
un ikh gedenk oyfn ershtn, oyfn meydele vos zi iz geshtorbn, Blume,

00:03:07.815 --> 00:03:13.002
un oyfn yingstn kind, vos iz alt geven eyn eyn a halb yor,

00:03:14.127 --> 00:03:16.744
oyf im gedenk ikh, er hot geheysn Nakhmen.

00:03:16.876 --> 00:03:18.869
di iberike gedenk ikh nisht.

00:03:20.948 --> 00:03:24.215
ikh vil fregn dir fun dayn lebn,

00:03:24.215 --> 00:03:26.682
ven du bist geven yung, in TYACHIV.

00:03:26.682 --> 00:03:29.548
vos konstu gedenken, vu hostu gevoynt?

00:03:29.576 --> 00:03:33.093
undz ze'mir gevezn a sakh kinder,

00:03:36.208 --> 00:03:38.473
undz ho'mir gevoynt in TYACHIV.

00:03:39.640 --> 00:03:44.774
demolts hot es geheysn, der

00:03:45.620 --> 00:03:51.617
oyf ungarish hot dos geheysn der VASHARTER, vu se hot geheysn, vu me hot gemakht di markn

00:03:51.780 --> 00:03:55.607
haynt veys ikh nisht vi azoy dort, vi azoy se heyst,

00:03:55.913 --> 00:03:57.397
un,

00:03:59.553 --> 00:04:02.717
ikh hob gehat a kindere lebn azoy

00:04:02.825 --> 00:04:07.829
normalish. mayn tate iz gevezn a mekler. er hot undz farzen mit

00:04:09.425 --> 00:04:14.723
kimat mit alemen. ober undz ze'mir nisht geven keyn raykhe mentshn. undz ze'mir oyfgevaksn in eyn shtub.

00:04:15.446 --> 00:04:17.739
du gedenkst di ADDRESS vu du host gevoynt?

00:04:17.266 --> 00:04:21.884
neyn. ikh gedenk di shtub, un ikh veys az se hot geheysn,

00:04:22.014 --> 00:04:26.830
di adre- di adres, de- deys hot geheysn VASHARTER.

00:04:27.276 --> 00:04:31.303
ober vi azoy dos hot, di adres, ikh gedenk nisht.

00:04:31.716 --> 00:04:32.916
un du host

00:04:32.916 --> 00:04:36.116
 du host gezogt az s- eyn shtub.

00:04:36.112 --> 00:04:40.138
dos eyn shtub hot geheysn eyn tsimer un eyn kokh

00:04:40.138 --> 00:04:42.000
un eyn verande.

00:04:42.175 --> 00:04:43.241
un ale UNK...

00:04:42.296 --> 00:04:48.000
un a keler. un ale ze'mir geven in eynem, afile oreme yinglekh vos zenen gekumen shnorn,

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.666
hobn oykhet gehat plats.

00:04:49.525 --> 00:04:52.059
un du host geshloft aleyn?

00:04:51.215 --> 00:04:55.200
neyn undz ho'mir geshlofn tsukopns un tsu fusns.

00:04:55.492 --> 00:04:56.526
mit dayn bruder?

00:04:56.218 --> 00:04:58.230
mit di briders.

00:04:59.892 --> 00:05:01.125
un du host gehat

00:05:02.392 --> 00:05:04.692
bobes un zeydes noent?

00:05:04.314 --> 00:05:06.553
yo ikh hob gehat,

00:05:06.553 --> 00:05:09.769
a babe mit a zeyde hob ikh gehat in Tetsh.

00:05:09.769 --> 00:05:14.846
un a babe mit a zeyde hob ikh gehat in Vermezif in RUSKE POLE.

00:05:15.067 --> 00:05:16.933
zey zenen gekumen a sakh ts-

00:05:16.722 --> 00:05:20.492
dey funem dorf zenen zey gekumen zeyer veynik.

00:05:20.492 --> 00:05:25.569
ober fun der, fun der shtot ze'mir gevezn in eynem. ikh gedenk oyf zey

00:05:25.569 --> 00:05:29.169
gut. mit zey ze'mir undz aroysgeforn.

00:05:29.126 --> 00:05:30.626
un vu hostu

00:05:30.626 --> 00:05:32.393
vos hostu geredt in der heym?

00:05:32.027 --> 00:05:33.323
yidish.

00:05:33.260 --> 00:05:34.106
bloyz?

00:05:33.907 --> 00:05:37.600
yidish, in yene yorn tshekhish.

00:05:38.274 --> 00:05:43.507
biz tsen yor hob ikh gekont perfekt tshekhish.

00:05:43.507 --> 00:05:49.246
un ungarish ho'mir alts gekont, vayl mir ho'mir gevoynt in an ungerishe shtot.

00:05:49.246 --> 00:05:51.830
un in di heym nor yidish.

00:05:54.041 --> 00:05:57.741
 emetser andersh hobn gevoyn- host gevoynt mit dir?

00:05:57.741 --> 00:05:59.274
bloyz di familye?

00:05:58.768 --> 00:06:00.800
nor di familye.

00:06:01.107 --> 00:06:04.274
du host geganen arayn in shul?

00:06:03.794 --> 00:06:07.384
yo ikh hob gehat dray tshekhishe shuln,

00:06:07.384 --> 00:06:09.092
un,

00:06:09.291 --> 00:06:13.569
az ikh hob gezogt az ikh bin bay di zibn yor, dos iz nisht

00:06:13.579 --> 00:06:16.584
azoy geven, vayl ikh bin geboyrn in september,

00:06:16.666 --> 00:06:19.092
far dem bin ikh arayn in z-

00:06:19.092 --> 00:06:24.415
iber a yor. ober, ikh hob gehat dray tshekhishe shuln,

00:06:24.415 --> 00:06:32.523
un a fir ukrainishe shuln, vayl di ungarn hobn undz nisht arayngenumen in di shuln in yene tsayt.

00:06:32.523 --> 00:06:36.969
un nokh dem iz opgehakt gevorn. in finef un, in fir un fertsiker yor...

00:06:36.840 --> 00:06:39.606
vi lang hostu geganen arayn in shul?

00:06:40.982 --> 00:06:43.769
zibn yor.

00:06:43.665 --> 00:06:45.298
du gedenkst vu

00:06:45.298 --> 00:06:47.031
di nomen fun di SCHOOLe, ober...

00:06:46.563 --> 00:06:51.676
neyn, deys iz gevezn PUBLIC shuln. lebn undz di andere shtub iz gevezn

00:06:51.676 --> 00:06:53.276
eyn shul,

00:06:53.300 --> 00:06:58.046
un di ukrainish a bisele vayter, ober dos ales geven PUBLIC shuln.

00:06:58.025 --> 00:07:00.192
du host geglaykht tsu geyn in SCHOOL?

00:07:00.353 --> 00:07:01.338
yo.

00:07:01.985 --> 00:07:04.185
vos hostu geglaykht tsu lernen?

00:07:02.046 --> 00:07:02.720
yo.

00:07:04.055 --> 00:07:07.015
ikh hob gehat a sakh khaloymes.

00:07:08.008 --> 00:07:10.974
du host gehat a sakh fraynt?

00:07:11.056 --> 00:07:11.641
yo.

00:07:12.045 --> 00:07:13.174
bloyz yidishe?

00:07:13.166 --> 00:07:14.513
bloyz yidishe.

00:07:14.548 --> 00:07:17.750
du host gegangen in SCHOOL mit andere oykhet, oder bloyz yidishe?

00:07:17.201 --> 00:07:20.984
neyn ze'mir gegan in shul mit goyishe oykh mit goyishe.

00:07:20.984 --> 00:07:26.107
bay di tshekhn mit goyishe, un bay di ukrainer oykh mit goyishe.

00:07:27.031 --> 00:07:31.169
dos iz nisht geven keyn ungarishe. di ungarishe hobn gehat ekstre shuln.

00:07:31.449 --> 00:07:35.116
du host gelernt fun yidishkeyt in SCHOOL?

00:07:34.815 --> 00:07:35.692
NO.

00:07:36.928 --> 00:07:40.800
ven zey hobn geleygt di tseylemes ho'mir undz aroysgegangen.

00:07:42.075 --> 00:07:42.905
un,

00:07:42.905 --> 00:07:44.182
dayn familye hot

00:07:44.182 --> 00:07:46.675
gegan tsu

00:07:46.675 --> 00:07:47.536
SYNAGOGUE?

00:07:47.507 --> 00:07:48.307
yo.

00:07:48.284 --> 00:07:49.007
ven?

00:07:49.523 --> 00:07:52.938
a yedn shabes iz mayn tate gegan mit di

00:07:52.938 --> 00:07:55.800
kleyne kinder, mit ale yingelekh.

00:07:56.315 --> 00:07:57.776
du host nisht geganen mit?

00:07:57.723 --> 00:07:58.661
neyn.

00:07:59.109 --> 00:08:01.292
ikh bin geboyrn,

00:08:01.292 --> 00:08:03.769
a meydele mit a defekt.

00:08:05.305 --> 00:08:09.830
un ikh bin shtark a sakh gevezn in di shpital.

00:08:10.075 --> 00:08:11.490
vos iz geven mit dir?

00:08:11.353 --> 00:08:15.984
ikh ho- bin geboyrn mit a defekt, in yene yorn

00:08:15.984 --> 00:08:20.649
zenen gevezn di geboyrn dos geb-,

00:08:20.649 --> 00:08:24.422
vu di kinder zaynen geboyrn gants primitiv.

00:08:24.422 --> 00:08:27.984
un me hot mir a tsi getun eyn zayt fun a

00:08:28.502 --> 00:08:30.797
fun a HIP.

00:08:30.797 --> 00:08:33.660
un ikh hob gehat a

00:08:33.660 --> 00:08:39.800
kleynem defekt, ober dem defekt iz men nisht gelofn zofort tsu keyn doktoyrim.

00:08:39.800 --> 00:08:44.784
un ven me hot in akht genumen shoyn, ven ikh bin alt gevezn an anderthalbn tsvey yor,

00:08:44.784 --> 00:08:47.569
iz es shoyn geven a bisele farshpetikt,

00:08:47.569 --> 00:08:50.261
bin ikh alts gevezn in shp-,

00:08:50.261 --> 00:08:52.390
nisht in shpitol, gips un geleygt,

00:08:52.390 --> 00:08:54.800
un ikh bin mer geforn,

00:08:54.800 --> 00:08:57.984
gefirt mikh in shpito-, in shul vu

00:08:57.984 --> 00:08:59.769
gegan oyf di fis.

00:08:59.769 --> 00:09:03.123
un vegn dem bin ikh nisht gegan vi me hot nisht gemuzt.

00:09:03.016 --> 00:09:04.585
host geganen oyf a yontev?

00:09:04.430 --> 00:09:08.184
yontev bin ikh gegan mit di mame in shul arayn, yo.

00:09:08.184 --> 00:09:11.292
yontev bin ikh alts gegan mit di mame in shul arayn.

00:09:11.235 --> 00:09:13.743
host gemakht a yontev o- ober a shabes in der heym?

00:09:13.179 --> 00:09:17.276
bayn undz iz gevezn KABALAT SHABAT.

00:09:20.578 --> 00:09:22.138
zeyer sheyn.

00:09:22.107 --> 00:09:23.507
vos hostu gegesn?

00:09:23.404 --> 00:09:26.532
zup un fleysh un fish un...

00:09:26.621 --> 00:09:30.467
ales deys vos es kert zikh tsum shabes

00:09:30.602 --> 00:09:35.375
iz gevezn bayn undz oyfn tish. mit khales, mayn mame hot gebakn khales.

00:09:36.645 --> 00:09:38.584
dayn mame, ver hot gekokht?

00:09:36.661 --> 00:09:37.722
iz gevezn...

00:09:38.251 --> 00:09:39.897
ales mayn mame hot ge-...

00:09:39.829 --> 00:09:41.056
du host geholfn?

00:09:40.640 --> 00:09:45.193
zeyer a sakh, fun kleynerheyt on hob ikh geholfn far mayn mame, yo.

00:09:45.193 --> 00:09:48.750
ikh hob geholfn afile bay di kinder ven zi hot gehat.

00:09:51.545 --> 00:09:53.653
vos hostu geglaykht tsu tun

00:09:53.653 --> 00:09:55.268
ven du host nisht geven in SCHOOL,

00:09:55.268 --> 00:09:57.253
un ven du host nisht geholfn dayn muter?

00:09:57.184 --> 00:09:59.920
ikh hob shtark lib gehat tsu leyenen.

00:09:59.920 --> 00:10:04.136
ikh hob geganvet fun mayn mamen di bikher vos ikh hob nisht getort leyenen,

00:10:04.136 --> 00:10:06.829
un ikh hob geleyenen di romanen mit,

00:10:06.829 --> 00:10:08.772
ikh hob libe gehat tsu leyenen.

00:10:08.772 --> 00:10:11.136
ikh hob geshribn a sakh, ikh hob geleyent.

00:10:11.136 --> 00:10:13.295
shraybn hob ikh haynt oykhet lib.

00:10:13.656 --> 00:10:14.718
andere zakhn?

00:10:14.709 --> 00:10:18.965
andere zakhn, hob ikh lib gehat shtark sht- in shtub.

00:10:19.561 --> 00:10:24.227
ikh hob geholfn a sakh roymen, ikh hob geholfn far di mame mit di kinder.

00:10:24.227 --> 00:10:26.306
ikh hob geholfn ales

00:10:26.203 --> 00:10:28.095
du host geshpilt mit di andere kinder?

00:10:26.306 --> 00:10:27.141
vos...

00:10:28.076 --> 00:10:30.488
yo, ikh bin geven a khevre-man.

00:10:32.311 --> 00:10:38.829
gornisht, mir ho'm-, in dem, in yene tsaytn nisht gevezn azoy vi haynt az s'iz gevezn kompyuters, s'iz geven azolkhe zakhn.

00:10:38.829 --> 00:10:41.465
s'iz geven andere zakhn vos s'hot undz

00:10:41.465 --> 00:10:43.284
ongefilt dos lebn.

00:10:43.284 --> 00:10:45.750
yo s'iz geven lebn undz a

00:10:45.750 --> 00:10:48.068
a TENNIS

00:10:48.068 --> 00:10:51.443
COURT, lebn di shtub nisht undzere

00:10:51.443 --> 00:10:55.920
fun di PUBLIC. ikh bin ahin a sakh aroysgegangen kukn nor.

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:58.318
s'iz gevezn vu me hot geforn oyf di

00:10:58.318 --> 00:11:01.511
vinter oyf di,

00:11:01.511 --> 00:11:04.465
KORCSO, vi azoy heyst es? veyst vos ikh meyn?

00:11:04.465 --> 00:11:05.772
di...

00:11:05.918 --> 00:11:06.850
oyfn shney.

00:11:06.772 --> 00:11:09.693
neyn neyn vos m'iz geforn oyf di, vos men leygt

00:11:09.693 --> 00:11:11.227
KORCSOLYA, vi azoy heyst es shoyn?

00:11:11.227 --> 00:11:13.056
SKATES, ah!

00:11:11.374 --> 00:11:13.113
SKATES.

00:11:13.056 --> 00:11:18.215
deys hob ikh gehat a pasyon tsu kukn. s'iz geven zakhn azelkhe, ze'mir zikh gegan bodn, s'iz geven,

00:11:18.215 --> 00:11:21.613
lebn undz iz gevezn der taykh, dos vaser

00:11:21.613 --> 00:11:23.102
s'hot geheysn

00:11:23.102 --> 00:11:24.068
Tisa.

00:11:24.068 --> 00:11:29.375
deys vaser. un s'iz geven andere zakhn vos hot undz ongefilt dos lebn. s'iz geven sheyn.

00:11:29.220 --> 00:11:30.451
du host gegangen oyf

00:11:30.451 --> 00:11:31.974
HOLIDAYS?

00:11:32.500 --> 00:11:35.443
demolts iz men nisht geforn aroys fun der shtot.

00:11:35.443 --> 00:11:40.465
HOLIDAY hot geheysn tsu geyn akht kilometer, az me hot undz avekgefirt tsu der babe.

00:11:40.465 --> 00:11:42.477
deys hot geheysn a HOLIDAY, keyne-...

00:11:41.730 --> 00:11:42.915
vi hostu gey-

00:11:42.915 --> 00:11:44.515
vi hostu geganen, tsu

00:11:44.515 --> 00:11:45.852
tsu fus, tsu...?

00:11:45.220 --> 00:11:47.863
neyn me hot undz gefirt mit a vogn.

00:11:48.319 --> 00:11:49.396
dayne vogn?

00:11:48.960 --> 00:11:53.329
neyn, neyn, neyn. me hot getun, geven emetsn ver es hot undz avekgefirt.

00:11:53.971 --> 00:11:58.761
dos iz geven akht kilometer fun di, vu der tate hot gehat di eltern.

00:11:58.658 --> 00:12:00.642
vos gedenkstu fun dayn foter?

00:12:02.727 --> 00:12:04.761
mayn tate iz gevezn

00:12:05.327 --> 00:12:09.704
zeyer a guter tate. zeyer a guter man.

00:12:09.788 --> 00:12:13.102
er hot getrakht shtark far di familye.

00:12:14.283 --> 00:12:15.637
vos hot er gearbet?

00:12:15.579 --> 00:12:18.988
er iz geven a mekler. er iz a sakh umgeforn.

00:12:18.988 --> 00:12:22.988
er iz gevorn keyn Tshekhoslovakye, er iz gevorn keyn Ungern, dort vu s'iz geven

00:12:22.988 --> 00:12:26.147
ofn me hot gekont forn iz er geforn, un er hot

00:12:26.147 --> 00:12:28.886
farkoyft un gekoyft un gemakht,

00:12:28.886 --> 00:12:31.079
un farzorgt di mishpokhe.

00:12:31.045 --> 00:12:32.060
un dayn muter?

00:12:31.894 --> 00:12:38.810
mayn mame hot nor mit di kinder. a yedes yor a kind, un deys hot men gedarft vaksn

00:12:38.966 --> 00:12:41.566
zi zi, zi hot geleyent?

00:12:41.775 --> 00:12:43.689
