zey hobn gemakht, zey vol-, zey hobn gevolt

00:24:17.069 --> 00:24:18.561
aroysgeyn, zey hobn,

00:24:18.561 --> 00:24:19.684
geshisn ober ts-

00:24:19.461 --> 00:24:22.846
NO, shisn,

00:24:19.684 --> 00:24:21.715
makhn epes...

00:24:22.846 --> 00:24:27.015
undz ho'mir nisht gehat keyn shtekenes, nisht keyn biksn.

00:24:29.523 --> 00:24:34.692
keyner hot nisht gebuntet, keyner oyf der velt nisht, ayeder geshvign.

00:24:34.692 --> 00:24:37.292
un vi di lemelekh.

00:24:37.508 --> 00:24:39.969
du host geven,

00:24:40.762 --> 00:24:44.886
 ven ven hobn mentshn aroysgeganen fun geto?

00:24:45.061 --> 00:24:49.123
men iz nisht aroysgegangen. funem geto hot men undz aroysgefirt.

00:24:49.123 --> 00:24:52.415
me hot undz aroysgefirt...

00:24:49.475 --> 00:24:50.393
ven?

00:24:53.861 --> 00:24:58.077
me hot undz aroysgef- se iz oykhet bay mir oyfgeshribn dort ales.

00:24:58.077 --> 00:25:02.246
me hot mir aroysge- me hot undz aroysgefirt in a oyf der nakht

00:25:02.246 --> 00:25:05.569
iz bayn undz gevezn in shtot a konzerv

00:25:05.569 --> 00:25:08.030
fabrik. fun frukhtn.

00:25:08.030 --> 00:25:10.200
vayl ven se iz geven a shtot

00:25:10.200 --> 00:25:13.000
un aringsum iz gevezn

00:25:13.000 --> 00:25:17.769
valdn, mit shtark a sakh epl, un s'iz gevezn

00:25:17.769 --> 00:25:21.477
di gantse velt hot gevust far undzere epl. zey zenen geven tayer

00:25:21.477 --> 00:25:24.753
vayl s'iz geven di tetsher epl, dos iz geven epes.

00:25:24.753 --> 00:25:30.646
un fun dort hot men gemakht fun epl azolkhe vos iz nisht gevezn, dos hot men gemakht konzervn.

00:25:30.646 --> 00:25:36.153
iz geven a fabrik fun konzervn, vos me hot oyfgearbet di frukhtn,

00:25:36.153 --> 00:25:39.538
un demolts hot men undz arayngefirt in dem

00:25:39.538 --> 00:25:41.046
konzervn

00:25:41.046 --> 00:25:46.492
fabrik's kelers. dos ibern gantsn fabrik iz geven a groyser keler,

00:25:46.492 --> 00:25:49.646
vu me hot arayngefirt, dos iz geven nisht oyf eyn mol,

00:25:49.646 --> 00:25:53.830
vayl dos iz nisht geven azoy groys. undz hot men avekgefirt in a bay nakht

00:25:53.830 --> 00:25:57.077
ikh hob nisht do dem dat pinktlekh,

00:25:57.077 --> 00:26:00.661
un me hot undz arayngefirt dort iz geven ful mit kestlekh,

00:26:00.661 --> 00:26:04.830
un oyf der erd, un dort ho'mir undz gedarft vartn dem

00:26:05.132 --> 00:26:07.085
vos hot men gez- zogt tsu dir?

00:26:05.409 --> 00:26:06.055
der

00:26:07.085 --> 00:26:08.239
vos hobn...

00:26:07.116 --> 00:26:07.538
?

00:26:08.246 --> 00:26:11.877
tsu mir, keyner gornisht, ikh bin gegangen mit di kinder mit di eltern mit di

00:26:11.877 --> 00:26:13.092
s'iz geven bayn undz...

00:26:11.934 --> 00:26:12.998
ver iz gekumen?

00:26:13.102 --> 00:26:15.369
emetser iz gekumen un gezogt az du muzt geyn?

00:26:14.953 --> 00:26:19.784
yo, me hot undz oysgeleydikt. s'iz gekumen, zeyere POLICE, di ungerishe

00:26:19.784 --> 00:26:22.338
POLICEn,

00:26:22.338 --> 00:26:24.830
dos hot geheysn demolts di zhandarn,

00:26:24.830 --> 00:26:27.830
un zey zenen gekumen, un zey hobn undz aroysgefirt

00:26:27.830 --> 00:26:29.815
ale fun,

00:26:29.815 --> 00:26:32.261
geheysn zikh shteln in di shure,

00:26:32.261 --> 00:26:36.077
un me hot undz gefirt vi di lemelekh aroys ahin.

00:26:36.077 --> 00:26:39.846
un zey hobn gezogt mir zol'mir zikh mitnemen nor kleyne peklekh,

00:26:39.846 --> 00:26:42.323
vayl undz vel'mir ales dort bakumen.

00:26:42.824 --> 00:26:45.132
zey hobn gezogt vu zey firn?

00:26:44.077 --> 00:26:46.923
zey hobn undz nisht gezogt, undz ho'mir gornisht gevust.

00:26:46.923 --> 00:26:49.123
zey hobn undz aroysgefirt

00:26:49.123 --> 00:26:51.661
ahin oyf der nakht,

00:26:51.661 --> 00:26:54.353
un di kinder zenen geven shtark mid,

00:26:54.353 --> 00:26:55.802
bay nakht

00:26:55.802 --> 00:27:00.030
un mayn tate hot genumen a kestl,

00:27:00.030 --> 00:27:03.430
fun epl, un hot arayngeleygt a,

00:27:03.430 --> 00:27:08.030
dos yingele dos kleyntshike fun anderthalbn yor, dos klenste,

00:27:08.030 --> 00:27:10.830
in kestl arayn, er hot untergeleygt shtroy.

00:27:10.830 --> 00:27:14.400
un er, dos kind hot zeyer geveynt, er zol shlofn.

00:27:14.400 --> 00:27:19.984
un s'iz tsugekumen an ungarishe goy, vos mir hobn im gut gekont, vos er hot dort gearbet,

00:27:19.984 --> 00:27:23.692
un er hot ibergekert dos kestl mitn kind.

00:27:28.892 --> 00:27:32.107
mayn tate hot demolts

00:27:32.107 --> 00:27:36.277
gevolt im hargenen. nor s'iz nisht geven zayn tsayt.

00:27:36.277 --> 00:27:38.938
nor er hot im geharget nokhn lager.

00:27:40.307 --> 00:27:43.738
ven er iz aheymgekumen hot er zikh mit im opgerekhnt.

00:27:43.738 --> 00:27:45.646
far togs hot men undz

00:27:45.631 --> 00:27:48.554
vu, vos hostu genumen mit mit dir?

00:27:48.553 --> 00:27:54.692
ikh gedenk nisht vos di mame hot ayngepakt, yeder hot gehat oyf zikh a kleyn pekele. a por kleyder a por

00:27:54.692 --> 00:27:56.123
ontsutun.

00:27:56.123 --> 00:28:02.892
di mame vos zi hot gehat alts ayngepakt dos esn, zeyer veynik iz gevezn, zeyer veynik ho'mir gekont trogn.

00:28:02.892 --> 00:28:04.353
un...

00:28:04.474 --> 00:28:06.074
ver iz geven mit dir?

00:28:06.077 --> 00:28:07.969
di gantse mishpokhe.

00:28:07.969 --> 00:28:11.907
di babe, di zeyde, ayeder eyner, ze'mir geven ale in eynem.

00:28:11.907 --> 00:28:14.384
di mume, di feter, mit di tsvey kinder.

00:28:14.384 --> 00:28:16.507
ale ze'mir gevezn in eynem.

00:28:17.507 --> 00:28:18.907
un

00:28:18.907 --> 00:28:22.584
vos hostu geven oyf oyf a ban ober...?

00:28:22.923 --> 00:28:25.430
yo, me hot undz arayngevorfn

00:28:25.430 --> 00:28:29.092
tsu fri in vagonen arayn. s'iz nokh gevezn nisht

00:28:29.092 --> 00:28:33.061
tsu fri, az di goy- me zol ay- me zol ayeder nisht zen,

00:28:33.061 --> 00:28:36.430
hot men, zey hobn zikh nisht geshemt, nisht far dem hobn zey dos gemakht,

00:28:36.430 --> 00:28:38.784
nor bay zey iz geven oysgerekhnt,

00:28:38.784 --> 00:28:41.277
hobn zey undz arayngevorfn in di vagonen.

00:28:41.298 --> 00:28:42.852
vifl mentshn?

00:28:53.271 --> 00:29:00.409
efsher fuftsik, efsher zibetsik, azoy vi di khayes.

00:29:00.409 --> 00:29:04.688
khayes hobn zey veyniker ge⟨UNK⟩.

00:29:13.630 --> 00:29:17.885
me hot undz arayngevorfn in di vagonen.

00:29:17.885 --> 00:29:21.311
di vagonen hobn ongehoybn mit undz tsu forn.

00:29:21.311 --> 00:29:24.688
kleyntshike fentsterlekh.

00:29:30.508 --> 00:29:35.327
me hot nisht gekont zikh oyfshteln keyn luft iz nisht geven.

00:29:35.327 --> 00:29:37.786
geforn shoyn a tog.

00:29:37.786 --> 00:29:40.557
mentshn hobn gebetn vaser.

00:29:40.557 --> 00:29:43.688
s'iz nisht gevezn shoyn keyn vaser di kinder zenen

00:29:43.688 --> 00:29:48.114
geven oysgetriknt undz ze'mir geven oysgetriknt.

00:29:49.393 --> 00:29:54.377
gepisht hot men in eyn top.

00:29:54.377 --> 00:29:59.065
un me hot es tsunamgemisht far di kinder un me hot zey gegebn tsu trinken.

00:29:59.885 --> 00:30:08.344
me ho'mir geflegt zikh shteln, dray tog ze'mir geforn, hot zikh geshtelt mit undz di vagonen,

00:30:09.983 --> 00:30:12.409
mir hobn nor vaser gebetn.

00:30:12.409 --> 00:30:14.885
un yeder vaser.

00:30:14.885 --> 00:30:20.098
me hot undz keyn vaser nisht gegebn. zey hobn getrunken di vasers, undz hot men nisht gegebn.

00:30:20.098 --> 00:30:23.491
oyfn dritn, oyfn tsveytn tog iz shoyn geven toyte.

00:30:25.081 --> 00:30:27.967
shoyn geven kinderlekh toyte shoyn gevezn

00:30:27.967 --> 00:30:32.081
mentshn vos zey hobn, zey zenen gekumen krankerheyt, vos zey hobn shoyn nisht oysgehaltn.

00:30:32.081 --> 00:30:34.901
s'iz geven a dokter vos er hot zikh arayngenumen

00:30:34.901 --> 00:30:37.672
sam mitn vayb, er hot zikh opgesamt.

00:30:37.672 --> 00:30:39.278
a rumenisher dokter,

00:30:39.278 --> 00:30:43.049
er hot dem tsveytn tog hot er zikh shoyn gesamt in vagon.

00:30:43.049 --> 00:30:45.983
er hot zikh mitgenumen arsen,

00:30:45.983 --> 00:30:51.213
un er hot es er hot dos oysgetrunken mitn vayb, ven er hot nor gehat dem fleshele.

00:30:51.295 --> 00:30:54.704
men vet oyfhern yetst a por minut, oystoyshn TAPE.

00:30:54.786 --> 00:30:56.786
BESEDER.
